@node Elf Racial Traits
@section Elf Racial Traits
@anchor{#elf-racial-traits}
@strong{+2 [Dexterity], +2 [Intelligence], --2 [Constitution]}: Elves are nimble, both in body and mind, but their form is frail.

@strong{Medium}: Elves are Medium creatures and have no bonuses or penalties due to their size.

@strong{Normal Speed}: Elves have a base speed of 30 feet.

@strong{@ref{#low-light-vision,Low-Light Vision}}: Elves can see twice as far as humans in conditions of dim light. See [Additional Rules].

@strong{Elven Immunities}: Elves are immune to magic sleep effects and get a +2 racial [saving throw] bonus against [enchantment] spells and effects.

@strong{Elven Magic}: Elves receive a +2 racial bonus on [caster level checks] made to overcome spell resistance. In addition, elves receive a +2 racial bonus on @ref{#spellcraft,Spellcraft} skill checks made to identify the properties of magic items.

