@strong{Time}: The process takes 1 hour per spell level. Cantrips (0 levels spells) take 30 minutes to record.

@strong{Space in the Spellbook}: A spell takes up one page of the spellbook per spell level. Even a 0-level spell (cantrip) takes one page. A spellbook has 100 pages.

