@strong{Light Undergrowth}: Consisting of scrubby, hardy bushes and cacti, light undergrowth functions as described for other terrain types.

@strong{Ice Sheet}: The ground is covered with slippery ice. It costs 2 squares of movement to enter a square covered by an ice sheet, and the DC of Acrobatics checks there increases by 5. A DC 10 Acrobatics check is required to run or charge across an ice sheet.

