@emph{Sniping}: If you've already successfully used Stealth at least 10 feet from your target, you can make one ranged attack and then immediately use Stealth again. You take a --20 penalty on your Stealth check to maintain your obscured location.

@emph{Creating a Diversion to Hide}: You can use Bluff to allow you to use Stealth. A successful Bluff check can give you the momentary diversion you need to attempt a Stealth check while people are aware of you.

